{"tid":1154593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】民主派遊行到特首辦要求會面","createTime":"2019-05-14T11:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T14:57:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70f84c6ca6b84a632419fa631db6505f8480070c","tid":1154593,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=347899&amp;refer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347899%26refer&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=dea82695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347899%26refer&h=fabd7c15\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=347899&amp;refer</a><br />\n<br />\n港聞<br />\n【逃犯條例】民主派遊行到特首辦要求會面<br />\n<br />\n5小時前  Share to Facebook<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】民主派議員遊行到特首辦，要求與行政長官林鄭月娥會面，擱置修訂逃犯條例。<br />\n<br />\n民主派議員毛孟靜、楊岳橋等一行14人，由立法會出發遊行至特首辦，沿途高叫口號。他們要求政府先擱置修訂逃犯條例，單一處理台灣殺人案，及與行政長官林鄭月娥會面。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦未有派員接請願信，他們將信放在特首辦外，由保安人員稍後處理。"},{"pid":"f93ab26905a14ac5fa8be88ac61fa90a4cfb74f3","tid":1154593,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"特首辦未有派員接請願信<br />\n<br />\n林鄭少家到"}]}